116
00:10:32,869 --> 00:10:37,569
gadis berambut cokelat itu melihatku.

117
00:11:09,569 --> 00:11:12,568
"Tampaknya aku memberimu terlalu banyak kebebasan sebelumnya."

118
00:11:12,569 --> 00:11:15,668
"Segera kembali padaku, Vermouth."

119
00:11:15,669 --> 00:11:18,469
